metadata.name: Infinite Hotdog Factory
metadata.description:
"I just wanna lie on the beach and eat hot dogs. That's all I ever wanted."â€”Kevin Malone in The Office

Are hotdogs the perfect food? I think about them a lot. It's meat and bread, and whatever else you feel like eating. Feeling like a salad? have a Chicago dog. Want to keep it simple? Just go with ketchup and mustard. Want something warm on a cold day? Put some chili on it.

I built this in Cinema 4D, Houdini, and Redshift. It took ten days solid of rendering time.
